The monumental "Royal Oak" of sports luxury watches that appeared in 1972. It has an octagonal bezel and is designed with a sense of unity from the case to the bracelet. Above all, this is 14790ST. Compared to its successor, it has a slightly smaller 36mm case.

There are some small scratches partially. Comes with a box (the outer box is dirty) and a warranty card. Simple adjustments and exterior finishing are performed.

Case diameter approx. 36 Arm circumference up to approx. 18.5cm

Minute markers around the outer rim. Dial Type: Analog. Luminescent hands and markers. Chronograph - sub-dials displaying: three- 60 seconds, 30 minutes, and tourbillion. Hand Wind movement. Calibre 2936 engine. Scratch resistant sapphire crystal. Screw down crown. Skeleton transparent exhibition see through case back. Case diameter: 44 mm. Case thickness: 13.20 mm. Round case shape. Water resistant at 200 meters / 660 feet. Functions: chronograph, hour, minute, second, tourbillon, chronograph, hour, minute, second.

Preowned - 15202ST.OO.0944ST.03 Audemars Piguet. This is a stylish and functional men's watch, made with high-quality stainless steel. The combination of the stainless steel case and bracelet give it a sleek and modern look, while the blue petite tapisserie dial adds a pop of color. The silver-tone hands and stick hour markers, along with the minute markers around the outer rim, make it easy to read the time. The luminescent hands and markers make it legible in low light conditions, and the date display at the 3 o'clock position adds a practical touch. The self-winding movement provides reliable timekeeping, with a 40-hour power reserve, and the scratch-resistant sapphire crystal and skeleton case back add to the watch's durability. Case diameter: 39 mm, thickness: 8 mm. The octagonal case shape, deployment clasp with push button, and water resistance of 50 meters (165 feet) make it suitable for various activities.



All preowned watches are not returnable. One year warranty for all watches. Preowned-15202ST.OO.0944ST.03 Audemars Piguet Stainless Steel Watch.
